videos.headline: Kentucky's Stoops reflects on win, breaking record
videos.description: After the No. 20 Wildcats down No. 12 Florida to give Mark Stoops the all-time school record for wins, he says: "I thought it was a thing of beauty."

videos.headline: UK grinds it out vs. Gators to give Stoops record
videos.description: No. 20 Kentucky goes on the road to knock off No. 12 Florida, 26-16, making Mark Stoops the winningest coach in school history.
